==Standard dialogue==
* '''Player:''' Hello youngster!
* '''Wilough:''' [I/We] don't talk to strange old people.
* '''Player:''' Hey who you calling old?! And strange?!
* {{tact|end}}

==Standard dialogue after paying him==
* '''Player:''' Hello again.
* '''Wilough:''' You think you're tough do you?
* '''Player:''' Pardon?
* '''Wilough:''' I can beat anyone up!
* '''Shilop:''' He can you know!
* '''Player:''' Really?
* {{tbox|The boy begins to jump around with his fists up. You decide it's best not to kill him just yet.}}
* {{tact|end}}

==Treasure Trails==
===Hard===
* {{tact|receives=a puzzle box}}
* '''Wilough:''' My brother reckons I can't solve this puzzle. I can't have him laughing at me! Do me a favour and solve it for me.
* {{tbox|pic=Puzzle box castle detail.png|Wilough has given you a puzzle box!}}
* {{tact|end}}

====While holding the puzzle box====
* {{tcond|If the puzzle box is not solved:}}
** '''Wilough:''' Sorry but you haven't solved the puzzle yet.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the puzzle box is solved:}}
** '''Wilough:''' Thanks [mister/miss]! <!-- He just says "Thanks!" when pronouns set to they/them -->
** {{tcond|When given another clue scroll:}}
*** {{tact|receives=another clue scroll}}
*** {{tbox|pic=Clue scroll (hard) detail.png|Wilough has given you another clue scroll!}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|When given a reward casket:}}
*** {{tact|receives=a reward casket}}
*** {{tbox|pic=Reward casket (hard) detail.png|You've obtained a casket!}}
*** {{tact|end}}
